{"tid":1801993,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"講下班魔警應對和你Shop方法","createTime":"2019-12-29T05:51:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T08:33:08.000Z","uid":76310,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"35c5e48d575708556d0ad36c058356fa7abce1fd","tid":1801993,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T05:51:13.000Z","msg":"講下班魔警應對和你Shop方法:<br />\n<br />\n1. 網上叫人帶玩具/帶魔法, 或者叫你裝修<br />\n商場好難走, 班魔警包圍晒出口, 或者外圍全包, 走唔到<br />\n直接入罪<br />\n<br />\n2. 亂拉人, 引你救人, 然後一大堆埋伏既便衣狗或防暴出黎捉<br />\n亂拉人, 引你救手足, 知道大家有義氣<br />\n然後極快速一大堆埋伏既便衣狗或防暴出黎捉人, 屈你襲警<br />\n可能你話, 你無委任證, 我點知你係唔係黑警<br />\n佢地總之有條罪入左你啦<br />\n<br />\n3. 直接濫捕, 見人就捉<br />\n見人就捉, 嚇到你驚<br />\n製造白色恐怖<br />\n然後配合網上5毛, 又送頭, 唔好再出<br />\n<br />\n4.砌生豬肉<br />\n鎖定邊個係手足, 然後便衣狗係手足附近破壞<br />\n防暴極速衝入, 話手足破壞, 砌生豬肉<br />\n<br />\n大家想什麼方法去應對"},{"pid":"e1ad87711ad2e2d6d03ea80d3414f77d4a172a23","tid":1801993,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T05:52:07.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈的障礙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801188</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dfbb2a02fe3be508c987eec53ae167ec80866d2c","tid":1801993,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T05:53:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8d0aeb08b92824ffedb1d6f2664eaa2135db49","tid":1801993,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T05:59:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aaed44e2dfb3e61f8bba3e0d6c563233341cc1a","tid":1801993,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:01:46.000Z","msg":"放工關心下佢地"},{"pid":"1219a3de03db134a177fef4ffd6196cb5f0c41b4","tid":1801993,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:03:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"275caa412e38a88edf9d2f9932495ea29f671af9","tid":1801993,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:39:14.000Z","msg":"唔再定邊日shop，小隊突襲中資舖(dump屎dump乜都好，總之有一下攻擊)or爆火警鐘後即走，自然會有防暴緊急進駐，依個時候就唔好再去"},{"pid":"779b7833198a6f70d27e4e50b22f9307bfa75146","tid":1801993,"uid":337336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:41:48.000Z","msg":"被捕電話勿解鎖，無野講，只係每隔一個鐘要講要打電話、要飲水、要去廁所；便衣狗無pass要反抗，唔好俾佢捉住你或推落地，下盤要穩，必要時要踢春袋，安全情況下要影低狗樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a2776fe2e9e7e59ad2f7931694ab1cc3856c1c","tid":1801993,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T06:43:41.000Z","msg":"好驚俾狗咬而慢慢變返港豬嘅唔該入一入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1800681\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1800681</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a53a380d891b46144637d9ec94621274808b19b6","tid":1801993,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T07:05:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />手足小心"},{"pid":"b6dbe86202304f075ae0eeedd101cd3b4377cf09","tid":1801993,"uid":10466,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T07:08:44.000Z","msg":"攻警曱宿舍，冇狗會叫人咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5398d7ef859cc8d9c64b48e6bdcd5dad38390e","tid":1801993,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T07:15:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2ea6bfe1db97dc80f5828a043b3a7322bfe85a2","tid":1801993,"uid":272569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T07:18:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b6398dadcea8ad96af712aac63157785ed65d07","tid":1801993,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T07:22:03.000Z","msg":"解決魔警應對和你shop 方法：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">彩</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">虹</span><span style=\"color: green;\">戰</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">衣</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">齋睇唔買</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">不停試身排隊但唔買</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">不停㩒飛但唔入去</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">齋坐食薑飲茶半個鐘再走</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人多其實好好玩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ffcccdaac23c760252e67eba2f3727bff384f0","tid":1801993,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T08:33:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}